      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Minister make these Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by section 2(2) of the European Communities Act 1972<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/>, paragraph 1(1) and (3) of schedule 2 of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/>, and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
         </formula>
